- The project has a component library and also a static website that uses the component library to provide information about something. They have around 30 40 sites like that. The idea was to add a command on their command line tool that when a unit will be run, it will generate anend-to-end test - start the browser, open a specific page, take a snapshot (an image), go to the second page, click a button, take a screenshot again.\
