- Re-reads the issue, reminds step by step that the test should run the command, use a specific library makes snapshots on all the pages. They also want to execute this test on all their landing pages. Then, it should add that test on the CI of the mentioned projects.\
- On top of the Overview there is a link to the PR. The reviewer follows the link and opens it in a new tab.\
- Then the reviewer sees there are some  discussion comments so wants to see those first.\
- The first comment from the author contains a description and example of how to use the command tool. The reviewer sees that they need to run the command with a specific url of where to run the website\
