- The reviewer wants to leave comments but the main review will happen on the call. They will look at the code together. The reviewer wants to teach the author that when you use a name it should do exactly what it says and let\'92s see how would you change this. The reviewer would let the author to write it on their own and it would be a live review process rather than asynchronous. So the reviewer can understand what is the author\'92s process of thought that make the author do the wrong things in the code.\
